flowchart TD

    A[Start System] --> B[User Login or Register]
    B --> C{Login Success?}
    C -->|No| D[Show Error]
    C -->|Yes| E[Go to Dashboard]

    E --> F[Create Product Type]
    F --> G[Create Product - SKU]
    G --> H[Create Stock In Batch - IN-001]
    H --> I[Start Scanning Serial Numbers]

    I --> J[Scan Serial Barcode]
    J --> K[Extract Serial Number]

    K --> L{Match Product?}
    L -->|No| M[Error: Product Not Found]
    L -->|Yes| N[Save Serial to DB - in_stock]

    N --> O[Create Transaction Type IN]
    O --> P{More Serials?}
    P -->|Yes| I
    P -->|No| Q[Finish Stock In Batch]

    Q --> R[Stock List Updated]

    R --> S[Process Stock Out - OUT-001]
    S --> T[Start Scan Serial Out]
    T --> U[Scan Serial Barcode]

    U --> V{Serial Exists?}
    V -->|No| W[Error: Serial Not Found]
    V -->|Yes| X{Status in_stock?}

    X -->|No| Y[Error: Already Out or Invalid]
    X -->|Yes| Z[Update to out_stock and Save Record]

    Z --> AA[Create Transaction Type OUT]
    AA --> AB{More Items?}
    AB -->|Yes| T
    AB -->|No| AC[Finish Stock Out Process]

    AC --> AD[Export Stock Reports Excel]
    AD --> AE[End]
